how to use pig:
http://n3xtchen.github.io/n3xtchen/hadoop/2014/02/18/hadoop-data-pig-programming

1 where condition:
SQL
SELECT * FROM mytable WHERE col1 > 20;
Pig
A = LOAD 'data' USING PigStorage() AS (col1:int, col2:chararray);
B = FILTER A BY col1 > 20;
DUMP B;
